%% Activity - Import bus data (admin)

flowchart TD
  Start((Start)) --> Upload["Admin uploads import file (CSV/JSON)"]
  Upload --> Validate["Validate file format & schema"]
  Validate -- Invalid --> Error["Show errors, abort"]
  Validate -- Valid --> Enqueue["Enqueue import job (celery/task queue)"]
  Enqueue --> Worker["Worker picks job"]
  Worker --> Parse["Parse records & validate each record"]
  Parse --> Upsert["Upsert BusRoute, BusStop, Relations"]
  Upsert --> Notify["Create import summary & send notification to admin"]
  Notify --> End((End))
